<c74object name='sp.controllerpitch' category='' module='SP-Tools'>
    <digest>Map pitches across a range in a given key/scale
</digest>
    <description>Map pitches across a range in a given key/scale.
</description>
    <discussion><h4><openfilelink filename="SP-Tools Overview.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
The <o>sp.controllerpitch</o> object takes incoming values (between 0. and 1.) and maps them across a specified range, including scale/key quantization. This is useful for creating melodic gestures from incoming descriptor or controller data.
</discussion>

